high_descs: turn around, go to end of center counter with green sponge
pick up green sponge from center counter
turn around, go forward to sink
place green sponge in sink to the right of white coffee mug, turn on water, pick up green sponge from sink
turn around, go forward past stove to black shelves in the right corner
place green sponge on front edge of black plate on second shelf
anns.task_desc: Place clean sponge on black plate on second shelf

high_descs: Turn around, move to the other side of the long table, turn left to face the sponge on the table.
Pick up the sponge on the table.
Turn around and bring the sponge to the sink.
Clean the sponge in the sink with water.
Bring the cleaned sponge to the left counter, turn left and bring the sponge to the wooden rack.
Put the cleaned sponge on the dirty plate on the middle shelf of the wooden rack.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge on a dirty plate on the wooden rack.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the end of the table to your left.
Pick up the sponge on the table..
Carrying the sponge, turn around and walk to the sink.
Place the sponge in the sink, turn on the water, clean the sponge with water, turn off the water then pick up the clean sponge.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelf in the corner to your right.
Place the sponge on the plate on the lower shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place the sponge on a plate on the lower shelf.
